title: Stage.com: *HOT* OshKosh B’Gosh Kid’s Clothing Just $4.99 Each (Regularly Up to $40)
text:
In addition to the *HOT* Carter’s deals I posted here , you can also head on over to Stage.com where they are offering up ALL OshKosh Clothing items for ONLY $4.99 each (regularly up to $40)! WOW! Please note that these OshKosh items are Cyber Deals and are excluded from additional discounts.
If you have a Stage store near you, be sure to choose the free ship-to-store option to bypass shipping charges; otherwise – shipping starts at $8.95 or is free on $49 orders.

If you’re shopping for other items, through 1/19, they are also offering up Buy 1 Get 1 Free Clearance items with promo code CLR at checkout (excludes cosmetics, fragrances, Spot On Values/yes! items, Doorbusters and Cyber Deals)! OR you can save an extra $10 off your $25 purchase with the code 10OFF or $20 off your $50 purchase with the code 20OFF at checkout (limit 1 code per order).
Score $4.99 Carter’s Clothing, $7.50 Toddler Jackets & More! (Thanks, Brandy!)
